    "We used Azure Cognitive Search for data indexing and retrieval.",
    "Using Azure OpenAI Studio, one can implement different strategies for retrieving the context chunks from the domain documentation and querying the LLMs.",
    "We use the 'default' setting and explicitly set the maximum number of context spans (k).",
    "Chunking allows limiting the information sent to the LLMs due to token limits.",
    "C. Project DetailsWe perform our evaluation on two projects in LIEF POST-P roj A and P roj B. P roj A deals with all the processes associated with the deliveries to the special value-added-tax regions for our industry partner."
